    "This is easily seen in the words selected in methods 1 and 2, but will be present in the synthetic text as well.",
    "This bias might be present in the model's understanding of sentiment.",
    "Future efforts could look at options for reducing unintended biases.Although this is synthetic data, care must be taken to ensure the exclusion of personal identifiable or confidential information, particularly if the data will be produced at scaled and used publicly.",
